title: Nicotinamide mononucleotide (NMN) as an anti-aging health product â€“ Promises and safety concerns
abstract: Elderly population has been progressively rising in the world, thus the demand for anti-aging heath products to assure longevity as well as to ameliorate age-related complications is also on the rise. Among various anti-aging health products, nicotinamide mononucleotide (NMN) has been gaining attentions of the consumers and the scientific community.
